00:10:29.470 --> 00:10:32.220
can get that allows this
user to make the decision

00:10:32.220 --> 00:10:34.250
to install and play your game.

00:10:34.250 --> 00:10:36.190
Now let's switch over
to the Play Games app.

00:10:36.190 --> 00:10:38.226
Fascinating feature
of this experience

00:10:38.226 --> 00:10:40.100
